    <summary type="html">&lt;ul class="simple"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;A house that fits me.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;A house were I can leave the windows open and not worry about rain coming in.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;A house that's warm in the winter and cool in the summer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;A house that has enough room for my books.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(More later.)&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
